        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme “Indira Gandhi National Vidhva Pension Yojana (IGNWPS)” Started On 7-10-2009 under the Social Justice and Empowerment Department, Government. of Rajasthan. Under this scheme, financial support is provided to the widows of the state of Rajasthan. A widow whose household is below the poverty line is eligible to get the benefits of the pension scheme. The beneficiary receives a monthly pension amount consisting of the Central and State governments&amp;#39; share.\n",
        "benefits_md": "\n- Women who are more than 40 to less than 75 years old monthly pension of ₹ 1000/-.\n- Women who are more than 75 years old monthly pension of ₹ 1500/-.\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "In the Indira Gandhi National Vidhva Pension Yojana (IGNWPS), financial support is provided to the widows of the state of Rajasthan.",
